id":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我第2個朋友運隻貓返香港好似用左2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2000係運費 許可證免費<br />\n不過如果真係鐘意既2000都唔係好甘姐<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔好甘我老母</span>"},{"pid":"b83d3a4b61602dc695b737e86140ec19f192e759","tid":250304,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似拎報告健康再申請運黎香港<br />\n不過真係會幾煩下<br />\n我fb follow開個美短又係台灣人黎 真係好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點都好過香港買<br />\n<br />\nBtw, ig係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFb係美短喵星人日記 應該無ig"},{"pid":"bda2899392424768175faba6dc214725e23f054a","tid":250304,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/22/125044_188ce005c3762f9d58224ae39a4e28df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2F125044_188ce005c3762f9d58224ae39a4e28df.jpg&h=3f73c89d&s={SIZE}\" />4000</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係純種<br />\n老豆係英短，媽係美短</blockquote><br />\n都夠哂可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我又唔係追一定要純種<br />\n只係唔鐘意唐貓<br />\n同埋美短痴人過英短<br />\n所以先想養美短"},{"pid":"0a2cb61cfda2baef1529a462f67f994d3d865fb3","tid":250304,"uid":23412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:35:16.000Z","msg":"其實蘇短係咪有混美短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲紋差唔多 但蘇短淺色好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/22/133514_35a6ad3d157c831001d6a0de96da32c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2F133514_35a6ad3d157c831001d6a0de96da32c7.jpg&h=df9fa19e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c8c0bfac7bdbaedd6f316f2397c335d4d2e2ec9","tid":250304,"uid":44928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"去cfa貓舍買既貓大多數都無先天性遺傳病既基因 後天既病就當然唔會保證話無 （google得知 有錯插細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n我都諗緊同私人繁殖既買家到買定cfa貓舍買 我就選擇左後者 始終對貓既健康安心啲 血統都純正啲 後者都怕啲人將啲貓亂交配 亂溝 睇果時就無野 養一排就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係就係貴啲 但貴在個安心同保證到 我覺係值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c96f3580e071ca39f705e5f69a0663b1721b952","tid":250304,"uid":44928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去cfa貓舍買既貓大多數都無先天性遺傳病既基因 後天既病就當然唔會保證話無 （google得知 有錯插細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n我都諗緊同私人繁殖既買家到買定cfa貓舍買 我就選擇左後者 始終對貓既健康安心啲 血統都純正啲 前者都怕啲人將啲貓亂交配 亂溝 睇果時就無野 養一排就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係就係貴啲 但貴在個安心同保證到 我覺係值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40931ce3a9f119cbea3ea72cc553d81739955ed9","tid":250304,"uid":44928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去cfa貓舍買既貓大多數都無先天性遺傳病既基因 後天既病就當然唔會保證話無 （google得知 有錯插細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n我都諗緊同私人繁殖既買家到買定cfa貓舍買 我就選擇左後者 始終對貓既健康安心啲 血統都純正啲 <span style=\"color: red;\">前者</span>都怕啲人將啲貓亂交配 亂溝 睇果時就無野 養一排就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/an